{"tid":986251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國醉男機上大鬧 空服員怒拿膠帶五花大綁","createTime":"2019-01-18T09:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T10:27:57.000Z","uid":32511,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ed9877c7e48a3a4eb6271d8956e8af51d0dd59ef","tid":986251,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVpTqG0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVpTqG0.png&h=0912c970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個泰國男子喝醉酒，在飛機上大鬧，空服員幾乎無法制伏他，全機還差點為他緊急降落蒙古！<br />\n <br />\n綜合外媒報導，當時這名26歲泰國醉男搭乘西伯利亞航空（S7 Airlines），班機準備從泰國曼谷飛往俄羅斯新西伯利亞，機上有158人，飛行時間將近8小時。醉男灌了半瓶威士忌，大約3小時後，酩酊大醉的他多次起身襲擊乘客，還動手攻擊空服員；空服員無可奈何，只好用膠帶將他的雙手和腳踝綁在一起。<br />\n <br />\n據了解，航班不提供酒類，酒是醉男自己帶的，而且他剛出獄沒多久又惹事；機長表示，本來還宣布可能會因為醉男迫降中國或蒙古，不過，他們最後決定將醉男五花大綁，抵達新西伯利亞再交由當地警方處理。"},{"pid":"2c646b638fbd9dfbd71413effb74de0ad5ebd942","tid":986251,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:40:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"556714139e5d2e2e5d696785d7b4e1eddf5fef1c","tid":986251,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"俄佬唔識咩叫以禮待人"},{"pid":"ca5371197b4f8027fcad6f49d2264bf14aef3185","tid":986251,"uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:57:18.000Z","msg":"S7空姐應該好好打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe4d54d7bb474f38f8f5966daeb70b9af263712","tid":986251,"uid":77580,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"泰國鄭中基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71adf3bf90e16d829049c214d7807e2a50dc703","tid":986251,"uid":146243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:58:51.000Z","msg":"可唔可以搵膠紙封埋啲垃圾bb個咀"},{"p